comments.body: Presume this is also a result of BCT now returning a different ordering when multiple candidates match rather than using the first. This does end up being a breaking change here, `bs[0].z` was allowed and is now an error.
Well, it was strange before and now it is even stranger. It may be that we need to revise the subtype rules here.
